{"type":"text","timestamp":1775863443715,"sessionID":"ses_2864b50cbffemkR4dKTU9zd1JD","part":{"id":"prt_d79b59d83001gkNJEU41SraGju","messageID":"msg_d79b56f42001N336J9ZIKQumxg","sessionID":"ses_2864b50cbffemkR4dKTU9zd1JD","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-022 — CLI publish 命令\n\n### Package Layout ✅\nAll required modules present:\n- `pyproject.toml` - ✅ Console script `kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"`\n- `agentcube/__init__.py` - ✅ Has `__version__` and exports all runtimes\n- `agentcube/cli/main.py` - ✅ Typer app with all commands (`pack`, `build`, `publish`, `invoke`, `status`)\n- `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` - ✅ `MetadataOptions` dataclass\n- `agentcube/runtime/*.py` - ✅ All 5 runtimes\n- `agentcube/services/*.py` - ✅ All services\n\n### Issues Found\n\n1. **Bug in `agentcube/cli/main.py:91`**: Duplicate `-f` flag in `pack` command\n   ```python\n   \"-f\",           # duplicate\n   \"--workspace\",\n   \"-f\",           # duplicate - should be removed\n   ```\n\n2. **Missing `agentcube/operations/__init__.py`** - Spec requires placeholder module docstring\n\n3. **Test failures (9 failed, 77 passed)**:\n   - 5 K8s provider tests: Mock mode not entering correctly when no kubeconfig\n   - 1 build version test: Off-by-one in version increment (`'1.0.0' in '1.0.1'`)\n   - 3 status runtime tests: Same K8s mock mode issue\n\n### Fix Required","time":{"start":1775863443712,"end":1775863443712}}}
